OL,7,FEverton FC have hit out strongly at
OL,8,F"threatening, racist and misogynistic"
OL,9,Fonline abuse directed at the wife of
OL,10,Fstriker Dominic Calvert-Lewin.
OL,12,FThe club said in a statement: "This
OL,13,Fsinister and intimidating behaviour is
OL,14,Fnot only deeply hurtful and
OL,15,Fdistressing, it is also criminal - and
OL,16,Fdoes not represent the values of
OL,17,FEverton or the overwhelming majority
OL,18,Fof our supporters."
