OL,7,F"The club urges anyone who sees or
OL,8,Fexperiences such behaviour to report
OL,9,Fit to the authorities and the relevant
OL,10,Fsocial media platforms immediately."
OL,12,FThe reaction from the club follows
OL,13,Fabusive and threatening posts directed
OL,14,Fat Sandra Calvert-Lewin. She has used
OL,15,Fher Instagram page to defend her
OL,16,Fhusband's record at Everton.
OL,18,FCalvert-Lewin, 28, whose contract
OL,19,Fexpires at the end of this season, has
OL,20,Ffallen out of favour with some fans at
OL,21,Fthe club.
